BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Category: Fitness\nSummer Swolestice is a 10-week strength challenge centered on community\, consistency\, and personal growth. Begin with a Lifting Evaluation to establish your starting point\, stay engaged through fitness classes and Lifting Socials\, and then return in Week 10 to re-test your lifts to see how far you’ve come! Earn raffle tickets throughout the challenge just by showing up and staying consistent with your training.\n\n\n\nIMPORTANT: This booking is your entry into the Summer Swolestice Challenge and THERE IS NO EVENT OCCURRING DURING THIS BOOKING TIME. Hit "Sign Up" to learn more about how to get started!\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/summer-swolestice-challenge?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoyNDg1OTU0NzE=&date=2026-08-05
DTEND:20260805T220000Z
LOCATION:Movement Portland
DTSTART:20260805T210000Z
SUMMARY:Summer Swolestice | multi-week strength challenge
