URL:https://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/summer-swolestice-challenge?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoyNDg1OTU0NzE=&date=2026-08-05
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Category: Fitness\nInstructor: Montana R.\nClass begins with a 30-minute strength training session focused on building muscle development\, core strength\, overall stability\, and metabolic conditioning. Expect to use dumbbells\, kettlebells\, and various fitness props. Class wraps with a 30-minute high-intensity circuit-style session that combines cardio\, mobility exercises\, and bodyweight strength conditioning in one session. The class may incorporate HIIT\, Tabata\, Cycling\, and Cardio drills.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/strength-bodyweight?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoxMzAyNzU0NTc=&date=2026-09-10
