DESCRIPTION:Category: Fitness\nInstructor: Taylor E.\nFunctional Strength Training for Climbers (FSTC) combines body weight training\, climbing specific movements and functional core work to improve strength\, balance\, and stability through the entire body\; including the legs\, back\, core and shoulders. This class also provides intentional mobility work to increase range of motion\, help you become a more agile\, and lessen the chance of injury in common areas where climbers tend to develop instability.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/functional-strength-training-for-climbers?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoxMzAyNzUyMzg=&date=2026-08-18
